ZH: 我家的木匠正在修理门窗。
EN: The carpenter at my house is repairing the doors and windows.

ZH: 这个木匠非常擅长制作家具。
EN: This carpenter is very skilled in making furniture.

ZH: 请问，你知道附近有没有好的木匠吗？
EN: Excuse me, do you know if there are any good carpenters nearby?

ZH: 这个木匠的手艺真的是一流的。
EN: The craftsmanship of this carpenter is truly exceptional.

ZH: 这位木匠已经在这个行业工作了十年。
EN: This carpenter has been working in this industry for ten years.

ZH: 他是一位本地著名的木匠。
EN: He is a renowned local carpenter.

ZH: 我姐姐的丈夫是一名木匠，专门制作修缮古建筑。
EN: My sister's husband is a carpenter who specializes in restoring ancient buildings.

ZH: 特别推荐这家木匠工作室，他们的作品都非常精美。
EN: I highly recommend this carpentry workshop, their work is all very exquisite.

ZH: 请叫一位木匠来修修这个烂桌子。
EN: Please call a carpenter to fix this broken table.

